rict matching (`getMatchingCoordinatesStrict`) while keeping the same output format.\\n\\n### Generating dependency graphs\\n\\nTo print deps.dev dependency graphs for resolved GAV coordinates while honoring the same `-Pcoordinates` filter semantics used by the harness:\\n\\n```console\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=all\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=group:artifact\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=group:artifact:version\\n./gradlew generateDependencyGraph -Pcoordinates=1/16\\n```\\n\\n[174 more lines in file. Use offset=121 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777519590557}}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.apache.kafka:kafka-clients:4.2.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-30T03-28-58-657200Z.log:318:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0bacd1669e1dd7350169f2cbe5e0d0819c8e2e94ada0512887\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp8svmAj5t7a2FlkWnUm7OYeNFhYSxY7DlHnzp17bZpVRCpQd-x-TTOh8HY_EGOnv9mKWmq-8WCJ4f-fsX1sqktjRLnY5g3K0nbi91rlRAlJy1Je8CRQa-iwUA8RistmStAlNrVXV7G_CZDwgBMB-vSsANgDBs5ke6C9xnjRsfN47Qkr25k1Uw412di17iDiibrvI3O2BVP18oReHbo_mzvvIEYXbb2a6mx7cLQ3ddqmDgxKlQMOBCmRazYzuaEwqHIFeRugnU8qNZbyyVZUy-TDXlIKj-TlR3xRkrlo0voPwFgUOFgAe7ooyEg4y7ucsGSEdsP_WzrC3fl2aC2mWGiTIGOcB5MrgP_9UmlkDlSP4OLrDCM_iLdxIIZ-An5aKruNso6uszlb66XRS3Gh7gFZpZcxCK5A6ZYdDzAGcbC-Et5SrQG4UfiEbWnfiImTMEbKUo_mSBA9naF9JqBXJxbDHO0YEKLQFNMs3K8isw1euOGynvn7YR5serE9mYc53rA7w7vss8EZR0308Pb5hnh6c_LsMxQjL2UJP39J3bsXjwyEIfe3nXdfvytLZg64UfF16pPdehRPvvTSHkzPYhTE26sF6jguJADU9dkvWXS9cqsUrud6mtSArhyMMXY1JZjZwz5MDt7SQlZw4gnCxeaqkNYbu23l50bViv97DNHbQ4iYsvZq21Pn_1cYJSA7k0_3gjdV2i6ZaVNOv8FHDB-PRVsGm8ooeXeCaSO9d-t20mz-cUxD6D-XUkJVVR6ocUUzP-rO8jss35pywajygmvKdyS4iiMj0WS8FdYPAQ8vdsglrgJOvuosJzqmW22p3YPpq3PwJPsn6crL-b2bxlIJ0omjIbZDPtDMg0HHqWs2LKf3rQAQVzUq9hC7Jfn0qqVwFSK4ZdiZsC5yn